"{\"uid\": \"rappler.com-sports-palestinian-skeet-shooter-juggles-anguish-pride-paris-olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  SUMMARY  This is AI generated summarization, which may have errors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9724383997161741, \"rank\": 0.02832815023723121, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, always refer to the full article.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MIXED EMOTIONS.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Skeet shooter Jorge Antonio Salhe of Palestine in action in the men's qualification at the Paris Olympics in France, August 2, 2024.\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 154, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Lopez-Fitzgerald\", \"score\": 0.9999996944935003, \"rank\": 2.6758614934798277e-07, \"text\": \"Antonio\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Lopez-Fitzgerald\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Lopez-Fitzgerald\"}, {\"begin\": 171, \"end\": 180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999591292133562, \"rank\": 2.764881847206345e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}, {\"begin\": 243, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9968636528618678, \"rank\": 0.003081535559468392, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amr Alfiky/Reuters  CHATEAUROUX, France - Born and raised in the Chilean capital Santiago, Jorge Antonio Salhe has never set foot in Palestine, the country he represented in skeet shooting at theParis Games.\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Lopez-Fitzgerald\", \"score\": 0.9999996944935003, \"rank\": 2.6758614934798277e-07, \"text\": \"Antonio\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Lopez-Fitzgerald\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Lopez-Fitzgerald\"}, {\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999591292133562, \"rank\": 2.764881847206345e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But distance has only made the heart grow fonder and more anguished for the first Palestinian shooter to appear at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.755878364144351, \"rank\": 0.32071614428457296, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Salhe did not make the final of the men's skeet event but just being able to compete at the Chateauroux Shooting Centre gave him a sense of fulfilment.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel very happy and proud to represent Palestine,\\\" the 49-year-old told Reuters.\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999591292133562, \"rank\": 2.764881847206345e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}, {\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999991682671, \"rank\": 8.316148252704827e-10, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a historic occasion to represent Palestine in Olympic shooting.\\\"\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999591292133562, \"rank\": 2.764881847206345e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Salhe's mother was born in Bethlehem and her family emigrated to Chile when she was four.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 949, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 6.854911369665803e-13, \"text\": \"Bethlehem\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\"}, {\"begin\": 987, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.999471276031181, \"rank\": 0.0005258478909730884, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His father was born in the South American country, which has the largest Palestinian community outside the Middle East.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.99988636685112, \"rank\": 0.00011152698938660016, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.755878364144351, \"rank\": 0.32071614428457296, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of my immediate family emigrated from Palestine to different countries around the world, particularly Latin America,\\\" Salhe said.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1177, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999591292133562, \"rank\": 2.764881847206345e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"However, there are still some relatives living in Palestine.\\\"\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999591292133562, \"rank\": 2.764881847206345e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The anxiety about their safety in particular prevented Salhe from savoring the greatest moment of his shooting career.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is impossible to leave aside the pain and suffering that my country is experiencing,\\\" he said, referring to theongoing conflict in Gaza.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1589, \"end\": 1593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"score\": 0.8115006652763049, \"rank\": 0.23228488004739473, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Due to the situation that Palestine has been experiencing for a long time, it is impossible to dedicate myself 100% to my sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999591292133562, \"rank\": 2.764881847206345e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The conflict has seen at least 39,400 Palestinians killed since Israel unleashed its offensive against Hamas in response to the October 7 attack on southern Israel that killed 1,200 people.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1766, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.6614865215769795, \"rank\": 0.5116101834455135, \"text\": \"Palestinians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 1792, \"end\": 1798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.999999813001995, \"rank\": 1.8473744824488525e-07, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 0.9999996669108087, \"rank\": 3.330892666443727e-07, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}, {\"begin\": 1885, \"end\": 1891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.999999813001995, \"rank\": 1.8473744824488525e-07, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An industrial civil engineer by profession, Salhe's introduction to shooting began with hunting trips with his father before he joined the Chilean Air Force Shooting Club in Santiago.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 2102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2058, \"end\": 2075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chilean_Air_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chilean Air Force\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chilean_Air_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chilean_Air_Force\"}, {\"begin\": 2093, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"score\": 0.9999999982417194, \"rank\": 7.915921900226039e-10, \"text\": \"Santiago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He may not have won a medal in Paris but Salhe said he considered his presence there an achievement in itself.\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2135, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999478139948184, \"rank\": 5.218872870691945e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because athletes like me are here, Palestine is present in the world's view and is not forgotten at a time like this,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2252, \"end\": 2261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999591292133562, \"rank\": 2.764881847206345e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately, I have not been to Palestine yet but I hope to be able to do so in the near future.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2381, \"end\": 2390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999591292133562, \"rank\": 2.764881847206345e-05, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": []}]}"